data.eml:eml: Diversity of Paranura Axelson, 1902 (Collembola: Neanuridae: Neanurinae) in Pacific Region of Russia and United States

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Smolis, Adrian, Deharveng, Louis (2015): Diversity of Paranura Axelson, 1902 (Collembola: Neanuridae: Neanurinae) in Pacific Region of Russia and United States. Zootaxa 4033 (2): 203-236, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4033.2.2
